data.description: Welcome to this cozy 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhouse, perfectly located near schools and I-25, with easy access to Fort Carson. This open concept layout creates a relaxed vibe, connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas with plenty of natural light. Upstairs, enjoy privacy with two bedrooms, each with its own bathroom. This home features hardwood floors on the main level and central air conditioning, perfect on those hot summer days.
